title: Toure Interview to Sex Dolls
itunes:title: Toure Interview to Sex Dolls
description:
Friday 1/19 - Today on the show we had writer/ journalist Toure stop by the show where he spoke on the memorable interview with R.Kelly in the early 2000's, the MeToo movement and more. Also, since it is Friday, and how people have been reacting to these high- tech sex dolls it was only right to open up the phone lines to discuss it for a "Freaky Freaky Friday" topic. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Kodak Black for getting arrested on 7 charges.
